# Zhao Family

## Family Overview

The Zhao Family is one of China's most respected and influential families.

Known for their wealth, education, and social influence, the Zhao name carries significant weight within elite society.

Unlike many powerful families, the Zhao siblings maintain unusually close relationships with one another despite the pressures placed upon them.

Family loyalty remains one of the family's defining characteristics.

